D300 Use triple double quotes `"""`
 --> D300.py:6:5
  |
6 |     'Sum\\mary."'
  |     ^^^^^^^^^^^^^
  |
help: Convert to triple double quotes

D300 [*] Use triple double quotes `"""`
  --> D300.py:10:5
   |
10 |     'Sum"\\mary.'
   |     ^^^^^^^^^^^^^
   |
help: Convert to triple double quotes
7  |
8  |
9  | def contains_quote():
   -     'Sum"\\mary.'
10 +     """Sum"\\mary."""
